msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe1886a146e1a0cbf994cf7e3031a6fc1cf68123","tid":1518292,"uid":72800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T08:55:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">中國嚴防嚴控國民政策預估 不定期更新</span></span><br />\n中國經濟 深圳代替香港 支爆 恐慌 貨幣戰 貿易戰 世界大戰 金融危機 走資 內地文宣紀錄<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1489149\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1489149</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中國糧食危機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/aeKPNuV\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aeKPNuV</a><br />\n#68 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n大豆 世界角力<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/aeKPNvV\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aeKPNvV</a><br />\n#69 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n全力谷內需 <br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/aeKPNyV\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aeKPNyV</a><br />\n#72 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3583591f5dceb26ef19e6fc76bb69fbb57b60bde","tid":1518292,"uid":166245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T10:19:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89b5e53e004f07257ef5d938e6150788364f5c64","tid":1518292,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T10:22:26.000Z","msg":"中共猶如暴秦<br />\n遲早搞到人變死士打柒佢地"},{"pid":"408e1e7e94d818df5a11919399d2d6f351ba9f91","tid":1518292,"uid":166245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89b5e53e004f07257ef5d938e6150788364f5c64","tid":1518292,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T10:22:26.000Z","msg":"中共猶如暴秦<br />\n遲早搞到人變死士打柒佢地"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T13:49:46.000Z","msg":"依家興搞公務員住宅附近嘅幼稚園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70f1e65acfebf196fa818cb575f48d77319664d2","tid":1518292,"uid":132037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"